<P>
   INDRANI, PERFORMER OF CLASSICAL INDIAN DANCE, DIES AT 68
</P>
<P>
   A5490 BC-OBIT-MARGOLIS-NYT 836 22:10 U A
</P>
<P>
   BEN MARGOLIS, 88, A LAWYER IN HOLLYWOOD BLACKLIST CASE
