<P>
   NEWS AND FEATURE SUMMARY -- No. 2519 -- Feb. 8, 1999 We are
offering the following articles for sale. Please contact us for
availability your country. Best regards, Karl Horwitz
</P>
<P>
   1. WE ARE OFFERING THE FOLLOWING ARTICLES ON THE LATE
</P>
<P>
   KING HUSSEIN OF JORDAN. PLEASE CONTACT US FOR MORE INFORMATION.
</P>
