   A. King Hussein and the Delicate Politics of Jordan
</P>
<P>
   By Lawrence Tal. From Foreign Affairs magazine. 4,000 words
</P>
<P>
   B. Uneasy Lies The Crown
</P>
<P>
   By Barry Rubin. From The Jerusalem Post. 1,500 words
</P>
<P>
   C. A Human Leader, King Hussein Made Many Mistakes
</P>
<P>
   By Gerald M. Steinberg. From The Jerusalem Post. 1,000 words
</P>
