<HEADLINE>
HOW TO CURB BORROWING: MAKE LENDING RISKIER 
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(bl)  
By LOUIS UCHITELLE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Ever since the global financial crisis began in East Asia 19
