</P>
<P>
   _ RICHARD PETROW
</P>
<P>
   INTERN ASSIGNMENT: Production assistant for national TV talk
show originating in New York City.
</P>
<P>
   RUDE AWAKENING: The intern is sexually harassed by a producer,
but gets a new internship after a complaint is lodged against the
offender.
</P>
<P>
   Log entry No. 1: J., the producer, kept telling me how great I
looked, and asked me out for a drink, and kept calling me ``Babe.''
