</P>
<P>
   Log entry No. 3: J., the producer, asked if I dyed my pubic
hair, and when I said, ``Pardon me?!'' he unzipped his fly and
threatened to show me his.
</P>
<P>
   INTERN ASSIGNMENT: Production assistant for a network TV news
magazine.
</P>
