<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-SOCSEC-STOCKS-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SOCIAL SECURITY ON WALL ST. : A BUY ORDER FOR $1 TRILLION
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review) 
(ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl)  
By DAVID E. ROSENBAUM   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
