at the funeral and praises him. By William A. Orme Jr.
</P>
<P>
   JORDAN-CLINTON (Amman) _ President Clinton and the American
delegation, their day. By John M. Broder.
</P>
<P>
   JORDAN-PALESTINIANS (Jerusalem) _ Palestinians have very mixed
feelings toward King Hussein and Jordan. By Joel Greenberg.
