</HEADLINE>
   (UPDATED Monday afternoon, following King Hussein's funeral)  
  
 EDITORS: IN LIGHT OF THE DEATH OF JORDAN'S KING HUSSEIN, WE OFFER
YOU THE FOLLOWING EXCELLENT ARTICLES FROM THE INDEPENDENT OF
LONDON. AT TIMES POIGNANT, AT TIMES PROVOCATIVE, THESE ARTICLES
SHOULD BE ``MUST-READS'' FOR YOUR COMMENTARY PAGES.)  
  
 (These TIMELY compelling ``separate buy'' articles are from the
Independent of London, distributed by the New York Times
Syndicate.)  
  
 (To publish any of these articles, they must be purchased from the
New York Times Syndicate's sales representative DEBRA WEYDERT at
732-390-4480, or fax her at 732-390-4697. Her e-mail address is
Debra/Weydert/CORPHQ/NYTIMES. If unable to reach Ms. Weydert,
please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at 816-822-1444.)  
  
