   Jordan's King Hussein is dead, having succumbed to his toughest
enemy, cancer. Saudi Arabia's King Fahd can barely stand, and
stumbles on the simplest sentences. Yasser Arafat suffers ever more
from the brain tumor inflicted after a near-fatal air crash.
