   OLYMPICS
</P>
<P>
   OLYSURVEY _ Half the American public thinks Samaranch should
resign and a third think the Games should be taken away from Salt
Lake City in light of allegations of the Olympic bribery scandal,
according to a survey being released Tuesday by an independent
marketing group. (Turner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   w/CAMPBELL-COLUMN _ ATLANTA _ Assertions that the hundreds of
boxes of Olympic records are uncatalogued are incorrect. Many are
inventoried, and I have details on gifts to IOC members and Billy
Payne's desire to keep some secret. (Campbell, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
