   FBN-AUBURN-FSU _ The fallout continues from Auburn's decision to
pull out of its Sept. 2 football game at Florida State. FSU
officials are scrambling to find an opponent to replace Auburn and
are considering legal action against the school. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 16.
</P>
