<P>
   BAPTISTS-PORNOGRAPHY &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ An X-rated Sunday school lesson? Not exactly. But
Southern Baptists have been talking about the ``secret sin'' of
pornography in their Sunday school classes nationwide. It's Topic
A. By JIM JONES. Story will move in ``a'' general news category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   L I F E S T Y L E &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
