discussed cutting them out of the debate on the way Los Angeles
trims its trees. Two City Council committees met Monday to
reconsider the way the city trims its trees _ the subject of long
and vocal criticism from residents, tree-lovers and professional
trimmers. By Deborah Sullivan. (Will move in ``n'' California news
