   JORDAN-FUNERAL (Amman, Jordan) _ United in loss and grief, an
extraordinary array of presidents, prime ministers and princes
gather here to accompany King Hussein on his final journey, as his
body is buried in a humble white shroud. By Douglas Jehl. (The
